     From the producer of "Goldfinger" comes a film widely recognized as one

     of the greatest spy thrillers of all time. "The Ipcress File" is the

     first film in the series of Harry Palmer mysteries, based on the 

     bestseller by Len Deighton, that made Michael Caine a star.

     

     directed by:



     Sidney J. Furie



     starring:

 

     Michael Caine  ....  Sergeant Harry Palmer 

     Nigel Green    ....  Major Dalby, Counter-intelligence bureau
